title: pc game, xbox game
description: Plants vs zombies is a very popular game, both on a computer and on xbox360 also. The game is fun to play whether your a young child or an adult. Its many levels and dozens of plants to fight the zombies with makes it enjoyable regardless of your age. If you enjoy this game, then you should also try plants vs zombies 2 and plants vs zombies on xbox360 live. Play alone or compete with other. Make your choice; are you a good guy or a bad zombie. Have fun !!!
